Sheyala, acompanied by her best of friends Sartha a fellow amazon, Madmartigan, and Anya the great White wolf, returned to her home.  Through a hard long battle she defeated Angelus and now holds the whole pendant.  The tortured souls of those that had been trapped were free to flow back to Hades' realm and finally rest in peace.  Through help of her friends Shey drove back the evil inhabiting her kingdom and she now works on rebuilding it.  The phoenix that died to give her power so long ago has been reborn and now lives inside of her.  Sheyala IS the phoenix, but at death the phoenix will be old nough to live on it's own, sheding the fire of light over the kingdom when she is gone.  Solemnly Sheyala promised that after Angelus was gone that the next war would be her last.  She too looks for release and it has been long deserved in her hurt and will to live.<br>
