<br>
Sheyala is not an immortal BUT she dies when she chooses to rest, or when she over exherts her magic(see the adept magic) As to the war on the MO board she is mortal. [she vowed one final war ~_^ I plan for sheyala to die on the MO so whomever wishes to be her end in a fair fight IM me(AIM sephykin14) or email me @ randyjerilacey@peoplepc.com thanks!]<br>
